Dieunerst Collin taught us the famous side eye. 👀 You might remember him as the Popeyes Kid Meme. He is now calling NE Ohio home as a lineman at Lake Erie College. Congrats on your success and thanks for swinging by the station!

@andrebernier caught me escaping the cold to match with the warm spots 😆

I dug out my pageant heels this weekend to help emcee the Miss Greater Cleveland pageant! It was so great seeing so many forever friends from the organization. And a huge congrats to the smart and talented young women who will now have the chance to compete at Miss Ohio! 👑
Not only is today Pi day…(3.14159…)but it’s #DressForStem 💜 A day to rock your purple attire to raise awareness for more women in science, technology, engineering, and math fields.

Couldn’t think of a better day (meteorological summer) to record a summer promo. ☀️ Coming soon to a screen near you 📺
We may have had a little too much fun (maybe some bad dance moves) filling and packing boxes with the Greater Cleveland Food Bank. Fox 8 was out volunteering today as part of Founders’ Day of Caring.
Family weekend getaway to Chautauqua Lake 🏄‍♀️

We have seen (and smelled) some of the worst air quality this week. A historically bad Canadian wildfire season has led to our hazy skies and prompted Air Quality Alerts. Thankfully 🙌 We are finally seeing a break and improvements the next few days💨
Look up tonight to catch a glimpse of the Full Buck Supermoon. 🌝
Hope your 4th of July is full of smiles and laughter. 🇺🇸 Happy Independence Day.

Honored to have taken a swing (literally my first golf swing ever) at the 27th Annual Jimmy Malone Scholarship Golf Classic. The work that Jimmy does to create scholarship and mentoring opportunities is so inspirational. Thank you for inviting me and to my team for being great teachers. ⛳️

☝️ Last year at this time, I stepped into the Dick Goddard Weather Center for my first day at Fox 8. I can’t believe how quickly a year flies by. Thank you for all the memories and support during my first year. Can’t wait to create many more. 📺
Happy National Ventriloquism Week! Wanted to celebrate in a special and nerdy way. Hope you enjoy 🤓
What the….hail. 🪨
Gals weekend in Chagrin 💕
July adventures ⛰️ 🍦 🌅
Baking and weather 🤝
I always look forward to foraging with my family for mushrooms each year 🍄. Not only do we have a blast, but my uncle always teaches us a few things along the way. Now…bring on the recipes.
Rocks 🪨 dust devil 🌪️ gal pals 👯‍♀️
Beach Bach! 🏝️ 💍 👰🏻‍♀️ An unforgettable weekend celebrating this beautiful bride to be. Can’t wait for the big day 💕
NE Ohio is no stranger to smaller earthquakes…but the one this past week was definitely felt across the area. Thankfully no damage or injuries were reported 🌍
Nothing to wine about here 🍷 😉 Had such a fun weekend exploring the wineries, trails and mountain of Oregon. Cheers to great friends for organizing @napleswineguy @gissainfante
Roxy and I were invited on the Carmen Cruiser this past week. We had so much fun with Ken and his crew covering Friday night football. 🏈

A weekend of celebrating and harvesting. 

She is married!! Congrats Jennifer and Teag. 💍 💕 Honored to have been there for your special day.
Have you seen any monarch butterflies this week? 🦋 If not, check out these amazing photos from @gabe_leidyphoto . I can’t stop looking at them!!
Hope everyone has a nice autumnal equinox 🍁
Hope everyone had a gourd 🎃 first weekend of fall! 😆

It was a beautiful night honoring an important cause…all while surrounded by good friends. Thank you to @rivchun_jewelers for inviting us to @ohioguidestone Evolution Gala this past weekend. It was incredible.

I’m STILL in shock!! 9 years ago I made an appearance at the Fox 8 studio as Miss Ohio. Yesterday, our talented producer @chrisgibilisco played back the memory. I guess Roxy made a great first impression 😉 😂  What a special memory and I’m so happy to now be working for the same station I visited years ago.

A bit of a late post but still soooo grateful and honored. A huge thank you to @clevelandmagazine and viewers for voting me into Cleveland’s Best Top 3 meteorologists. Congrats to my many other coworkers who also made the list…Natalie, Stefani, Wayne, Todd, Ken…just to name a few. It is so cool to be recognized for something I love doing and to even be included with some of the best in the biz. @betsykling @markjweather
Have you found a woollybear this fall? 🐛
Happy Woollybear Sunday 🤎🧡🖤
Lake Erie is a world record holder for the most waterspouts in a 24 hour period. The International Centre for Waterspout Research recorded over 180 waterspouts on Oct 7th. 🌪️
Weekend leaf peepin’ 🍁

Midges are everywhere!!! 🦟 While they are beneficial…I think we are ready for them to scoot on out of here. They finally will stop hatching and become more dormant when the lake drops into the 40s and colder.
Just your friendly neighborhood ghost 👻 Don’t worry…there were plenty of treats.
What’s better than just plain old snow…Thundersnow!!!!

Loved reconnecting with my Miss Ohio friends and family this weekend while judging Miss Maple City. Congrats to the new Miss Maple City @misslegenza and Miss Maple City Teen @cassie.mattson ! Everyone did an amazing job…best of luck at Miss Ohio this summer 👑
These fun clouds were spotted across our area last Wednesday ahead of some rain. 🌧️ did you spot them?
From being my Miss Ohio Teen to Mrs John 👑  Rosie, it was an honor to be there and celebrate your special day. 💕
Happy gobbling 🦃
Feeling just like this turkey…stuffed 😆 🦃 Happy Thanksgiving! Hope you had a beautiful holiday.

Sisters 🖤
